title: Manny Pacquiao vs. Yordenis Ugas: First Look Highlights | PBC ON FOX
author: PBC ON FOX
description:
Watch the first look at some of the best moments between Manny Pacquiao and Yordenis Ugas' WBA Welterweight title fight. These two fought with non-stop action from Las Vegas, but Ugas was the victorious one. Don't forget to buy the Pacquiao vs. Ugas PPV: https://foxs.pt/3ifl0lJ
